{
  "stem": "18670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even to the last minute, we wanted to be-- do honest business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started off first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the one that after I'd come home, my father sent me back to Vienna to see whether there was any way of getting out of Austria, because we were hoping to get affidavits from America, from my father-- my mother's family, our grandfather.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we also felt there wasn't any future, because the livelihood was gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncle's business was different in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did tremendous amount of business when the Nazis came in, because--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Men's clothing and ladies clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were buying-- in Nazi Germany, they had shortages already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here in Vienna, they had everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in and they bought, bought.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then within a few weeks, my uncle had a commissar put into his store.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The guy controlled-- he used to be a tailor working for him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The guy became the boss now, controlled the business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually they did leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were the first one to plan it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just plain Nazis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The stormtroopers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the funny thing is that most of the offensive things that were done, really offensive to Jews, were not done by the German Army that came in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was done by Austrian Nazis, some in uniform, some not in uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- first of all, you had to have an Aryan pass to have a swastika, have the Hakenkrusz the Germans call it, to wear the pin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you wore it, you had to-- again, there were spot checks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to show your Aryan papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They issued papers that you're an Aryan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people were rounded up in the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were taken out of the houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were going from house to house, apartment houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
